trans-unit.source: Contains the values of a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult"></xref> property.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder verdiene i en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult"> </xref> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> instances are similar to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> instances.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>forekomster er lik <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>forekomster.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry></xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>

trans-unit.source: The notable difference is that the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> retrieves its information from the Active Directory Domain Services hierarchy each time a new object is accessed, whereas the data for the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> is already available in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection> that a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> query returns.
trans-unit.target: Viktige forskjellen er at den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>henter informasjon fra Active Directory Domain Services-hierarkiet hver gang en ny objektet er åpnet, mens dataene for den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>finnes allerede i den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection>som en <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher>spørringen returnerer.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResultCollection> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>

trans-unit.source: If you try to get a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult> property that your query did not specify for retrieval, the property will not be available.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du prøver å få en <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>egenskapen spørringen ikke har angitt for henting av egenskapen blir ikke tilgjengelig.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchResult>

trans-unit.source: The Contains method determines whether a specified property value is in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains bestemmer om en egenskapsverdi for angitt i denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The property value to find.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien til å finne.

trans-unit.source: The return value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified property belongs to this collection; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returverdien er <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> hvis den angitte egenskapen tilhører denne samlingen; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method copies the property values from this collection to an array, starting at a particular index of the array.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo overfører egenskapsverdiene fra samlingen til en matrise, med Start fra en bestemt indeks i matrisen.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref:System.Object> that receives this collection's property values.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av typen <xref:System.Object>som mottar egenskapsverdiene for denne samlingen.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based array index at which to begin copying the property values.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen nullbasert matrise som du vil kopiere egenskapsverdiene.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method retrieves the index of a specified property value in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf henter indeksen for en angitt egenskapsverdi i denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The property value to find.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien til å finne.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the specified property value.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for den angitte egenskapsverdien.

trans-unit.source: If the object is not found, the return value is -1.
trans-unit.target: Hvis objektet ikke finnes, er returverdien -1.

trans-unit.source: The Item property gets the property value that is located at a specified index.
trans-unit.target: Elementegenskapen henter egenskapsverdi som er plassert på en angitt indeks.

trans-unit.source: In C#, this property is the indexer for the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er i C#, indekserer for <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection>klasse.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.ResultPropertyValueCollection>

trans-unit.source: In JScript, you can use the default indexed properties defined by a type, but you cannot explicitly define your own.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke indekserte standardegenskaper som er definert av en type i JScript, men du kan angi din egen.

trans-unit.source: However, specifying the expando attribute on a class automatically provides a default indexed property with a type of Object and an index type of <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Angir attributtet expando på en klasse gir automatisk standard imidlertid indeksert egenskap med en objekttypen og en indekstype <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the property value to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for å hente egenskapsverdien.

trans-unit.source: The property value that is located at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien som er plassert i den angitte indeksen.
